post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-bad-deeds-al-sayyiat","tag-expiation-al-kaffarah","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-manners-adab","tag-night-prayer-al-tahajjud","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-righteous-predecessors-salaf-as-salih","tag-solitude-khalwah","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-a2j","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":10872,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/02\/ahl-al-kitab-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ahl Kitab: Among People of the Book are righteous believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, delayed the evening prayer, then he later came out to the mosque to find people waiting for the prayer. The Prophet said, \u201cAre there none among the people of these religions remembering Allah at this hour besides\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/02\/07\/prophets-righteous-pure-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":1},"title":"Fudayl on Tazkiyyah: Prophets and righteous have pure hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIt has been said that among the character of the prophets and chosen elect is the purity of their hearts. They are three characteristics: forbearance, penitence, and a portion of prayer in the night.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20528,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/04\/01\/guide-me-good-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: O Allah, guide me to righteous character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, my prayer, my rites, my life, and my death are for Allah the Lord of the worlds. He has no partner and with this I have been commanded and I am among the Muslims.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/18\/prophet-supplicates-good-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Supplication for good character after prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: I never prayed behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while I was near to him but that I would hear him say at the end of every prayer, \u201cO Allah, forgive all of my sins and mistakes. O Allah, refresh me and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19589,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/seven-five-takbir-salat-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Seven and five Takbir in Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Awf reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pronounce takbir during the Eid prayer seven times before the recitation in the first cycle, and five times before the recitation in the second cycle. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThis tradition is acted upon by some of the people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28430,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/28\/cure-heart-five\/","url_meta":{"origin":38583,"position":5},"title":"Ibrahim on Healing: Medicine for the soul is in five things","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Azdi reported: Ibrahim al-Khawwas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe cure of the heart is in five things: reading the Quran with contemplation, emptying the stomach, standing for prayer at night, humbly supplicating at dawn, and sitting with the righteous.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 15767 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u0623\u064e\u0632\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"te